text: Hrvoje Benić (born 26 April 1992) is a Croatian water polo player for VK Jug and the Croatian national team. He participated at the 2019 World Championships. ==See also== * List of World Aquatics Championships medalists in water polo ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male water polo players Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in water polo
